ch fails to compile (missing IMarshal/marshaler). Need to adjust Cargo.toml (pin windows/windows-core/windows-future or usn-journal-rs) once PinkSnow reservation ends. Leaving Cargo.lock generated by latest resolve; will revisit and fix as soon as manifests are free.","created_at":"2025-11-21T01:30:12Z"},{"id":85,"issue_id":"ultrasearch-c00.1","author":"ubuntu","text":"Resolved windows-future compile break by removing unused usn-journal-rs from workspace/ntfs-watcher (made optional feature and dropped workspace dep). Workspace now on windows 0.58 + sysinfo 0.30.13; cargo check/clippy/fmt all green.","created_at":"2025-11-21T01:40:57Z"}]}
